Soft-shoulder jackets and wide, pressed-crease trousers in fluid wovens — tailoring language without the armour.

## Who''s showing it
Consistent across The Row, Toteme and Saint Laurent resort; filtering into contemporary via St. Agni and Rohe.

## Materials & making
Fluid viscose-linen blends, sand-washed cupro, heavier silk twill. Our Tangier trouser block already speaks this language.

## Wear it forward
- Cut the Tangier trouser in the Kurabo chambray for a softer read
- One soft blazer, not a suiting program
- Press creases, no shoulder-pad tooling needed', '["https://www.vogue.com/fashion-shows"]', '[{"label":"soft-shoulder blazer"},{"label":"wide pressed-crease trouser"},{"label":"sand-washed cupro"}]', 'exploring', 1, '2026-07-05 07:44:00') ON CONFLICT(id) DO UPDATE SET title = excluded.title, season = excluded.season, focus = excluded.focus, brief_md = excluded.brief_md, citations = excluded.citations, items = excluded.items, status = excluded.status, watch = excluded.watch, last_researched_at = excluded.last_researched_at;
INSERT OR REPLACE INTO brand_brain (id, mode, status, answers_json, checklist_json, onboarded, updated_at) VALUES ('brain', 'new', 'draft', '{"brand.name":"Maison Atlantique","brand.category":"Elevated coastal resortwear — linen-forward separates and easy dresses","brand.target":"The woman who plans her year around the sea. She summers in Tangier, Comporta or the Aegean, buys few things well, and wants to look composed from the morning market to a late dinner without a suitcase of options.","brand.feeling":"A whitewashed riad at golden hour — warm stone, sea air, linen moving in the breeze. Unhurried, sun-worn, quietly expensive.","brand.gap":"Resortwear splits in two: disposable holiday fast-fashion, and €900 designer vacation pieces. Almost nothing in between is genuinely well-made, honestly sourced, and priced for a woman who takes two good trips a year rather than ten. Maison Atlantique owns that middle — Mediterranean-made, transparent, built to outlast the season.","brand.rejects":"Logo-driven, trend-chasing poolside costume. Nothing that only works on holiday.","brand.thesis":"Maison Atlantique makes elevated coastal resortwear for women who dress around the sea — linen-forward separates and easy dresses, made in Morocco and Portugal, priced in the honest gap between disposable holiday clothes and designer vacationwear. Few pieces, done properly, that read as composed from the beach to a late dinner and last far beyond one summer.","brand.words":["sun-worn","composed","linen","Mediterranean","unhurried","tactile","warm","considered","coastal","honest","timeless","easy"],"brand.antiWords":["poolside","logo","fast","costume","disposable","loud"],"brand.references":["Marrakshi Life","Toteme","St. Agni","Rohe","Cawley"],"brand.voice":"Warm, plain and quietly assured — like a well-travelled friend who knows the good tailor in Tangier. No hype, no exclamation marks. We talk about cloth, provenance and how a piece wears in five summers, not about trends.","brand.palette":["chalk","warm sand","terracotta","saffron","faded indigo","olive"],"brand.type":"A warm humanist serif for the wordmark, a quiet grotesque sans for everything else — editorial but unfussy.","collection.skuCount":"9 styles at launch","collection.categories":["Trousers","Shirting","Dresses","Knitwear","Cover-ups","Skirts"],"collection.hero":"The Tangier Trouser — a wide, pressed-crease linen trouser in Libeco heritage cloth","collection.colorways":"2–3 per style (chalk, warm sand, and one seasonal — SS27 is a faded-indigo chambray)","collection.calendar":"Seasonal (SS/AW)","design.concept":"A wide-leg, high-rise linen trouser with a pressed crease and a soft, unstructured waistband — heritage Belgian linen the colour of warm chalk, photographed on sun-warmed stone at golden hour.","prod.region":"Morocco","prod.regionWhy":"Our makers are in Marrakech, Tangier and Casablanca — genuine small-batch ateliers that run 100-unit orders — plus a real duty story: the EU–Morocco association agreement means zero duty into the EU with an EUR.1 certificate, and yarn-forward Moroccan cloth qualifies for US GSP review. Short freight, and a Mediterranean-made narrative that IS the brand.","prod.moq":"Fewer styles at higher depth. 9 styles, ~120 units each at launch, part-funded by a pre-order window on the two hero pieces. One blanket linen order across the trouser and shirting to clear the mill MOQ once.","prod.fabrics":["Libeco heritage linen (BE)","Somelos cotton poplin (PT)","Atlas loop-back terry (MA)","Bursa viscose crepe (TR)","Kurabo 4.5oz chambray (JP)"],"prod.sampleRounds":"3","cost.markets":["European Union","United Kingdom","United States"],"cost.dutyNotes":"EU: zero duty from Morocco with an EUR.1 movement certificate (association agreement). US: linen apparel ~14–16% MFN; pursuing yarn-forward/GSP qualification on the Moroccan canvas styles. UK: factor ~12% on MA-origin post-Brexit.","cost.avgRetail":"€145 average, €95–€320 range","cost.targetMargin":"62% DTC gross margin","cost.wholesale":"Selective only — keystone (2.2–2.5×) to a short list of coastal boutiques; never below 55% of our own retail.","commerce.phase":"DTC + selective wholesale","commerce.preorder":"A 3-week pre-order window on the two hero styles before the drop — charge at order, cap at production depth, no discount (early access is the incentive). Funds the first cut.","commerce.fulfilment":"Self-ship from the Marrakech studio for launch; move to an EU 3PL (Portugal) once volume justifies it.","launch.date":"May 2027 (ahead of the northern-hemisphere summer)","launch.listGoal":"3,000 pre-launch emails","launch.campaign":"\"Dressed for the sea\" — a quiet campaign shot on location on the Atlantic coast of Morocco: the same nine pieces worn from morning market to late dinner, maker and provenance named on every look. Lead with the Tangier Trouser.","fin.budget":"€45,000 launch budget","fin.launchUnits":"~1,080 units (9 styles × ~120)","fin.risks":["Single production region — build a Portugal backup for shirting","Summer-timed demand is narrow — extend with trans-seasonal linen and a small AW capsule","Cold-start audience — six months of pre-launch content and the pre-order list before the drop","Linen MOQ ties up cash — blanket order plus pre-order funding to de-risk"]}', '{}', 1, '2026-07-08 09:00:00');
